sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant A as Drogon API
    participant M as Collection Manager
    participant H as HNSW index
    participant S as SQ re-rank
    participant F as Payload filter

    C->>A: POST /collections/{c}/points/search
    A->>M: lookup collection (read lock)
    M->>H: search(query, k x over-fetch)
    H-->>M: candidate ids
    M->>S: re-rank with exact distances
    S-->>M: refined top-k
    M->>F: apply payload filter (must / should)
    F-->>M: filtered hits
    M-->>A: results + payloads
    A-->>C: 200 JSON
